of this Hou&s;e. So help me God!&endq; It was provided
that the &s;aid paper or &s;chedule, with the oath afore&s;aid,
&s;hould be carefully kept by the clerk, to be in&s;pected by
the members of the Hou&s;e of Commons, without fee or
