<HEAD>CHAP. XIV.</HEAD>
<HEAD TYPE="sub">&sect; I. Exploit of the Swedes in Pomerania. &sect; II. Skirmi&s;hes
between the Pru&s;&s;ians and Au&s;trians in Saxony. &sect; III.
